short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Todo list with some extra features

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can make a note of what you want to search for at that time so that you don't forget it.
When you search for content in the list, it automatically deletes it.

You can use more easily if you register keyboard shortcut and pin it.
